ku.com/sniper-elite-resistance-games-pc-ps5-best-1851747402?rev=1737768811350\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/sniper-elite-resistance-games-pc-ps5-best-1851747402?rev=1737768811350\"\u003etense, stealth-focused gameplay\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e fans have come to know and love. As with all the games in the series, you can expect a fairly lengthy campaign with plenty of different ways to approach your objectives.  - Billy Givens \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/sniper-elite-resistance-how-long-campaign-difficulty-1851749581\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/sniper-elite-resistance-how-long-campaign-difficulty-1851749581\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"73b283c41fec275866ee1dfff29117af\" data-recommend-id=\"image://73b283c41fec275866ee1dfff29117af\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A sniper fires a gun while hiding admist the wreckage of war.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"A sniper fires a gun while hiding admist the wreckage of war.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"false\" data-imagerights=\"other-license\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/73b283c41fec275866ee1dfff29117af.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/73b283c41fec275866ee1dfff29117af.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: